This paper deals with the task of extracting personality traits from text, which is a natural language processing (NLP) problem. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP and related topics. The paper also uses machine learning models, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with data annotation and reliability, which could place it in cs.CY (Computers and Society) or cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
